{"tid":1253292,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"英國美國既家庭會唔會為政見嘈交?","createTime":"2019-06-23T13:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T08:52:14.000Z","uid":54930,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"d9352636bc32350f11761c42d40fb83dbc16c9fd","tid":1253292,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T13:20:39.000Z","msg":"例如英國後生支持留歐,上一代支持脫歐<br />\n或者美國後生支持希拉莉,上一代支持侵侵<br />\n<br />\n佢地會唔會好似香港家庭嘈交<br />\n跟住比人趕出門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c5f01f7a5a0381728e9b91b425fbbfb92ed4260","tid":1253292,"uid":38904,"like":131,"dislike":3,"score":128,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T13:23:14.000Z","msg":"歐美啲人覺得你係屬於一個個體<br />\n你支持啲乜同你老豆老母冇關<br />\n<br />\n華人覺得物以類聚, 自己身邊嘅人應該要同一立場"},{"pid":"4df915ef5dba4d0cd95cff113894d597d10a802f","tid":1253292,"uid":267838,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T13:26:22.000Z","msg":"會，我男友成日同佢老豆嘈<br />\n但係嘈完就無嘢<br />\n佢地由細就教要獨立思考同埋唔同意見<br />\n<br />\n唔似香港咁要個個人倒模咁"},{"pid":"cf9c4afa57adedaa2d8b49739163326c45fbbfa1","tid":1253292,"uid":66669,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T13:51:36.000Z","msg":"會，嘈到搬走都會"},{"pid":"5f709eb38ccc5db693989da1ae3125e7cddaf857","tid":1253292,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:16:46.000Z","msg":"會唔會廢老前廢老後？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"154dc7a301dfe575265cdbb26a76298cdc7ece3e","tid":1253292,"uid":46151,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:50:46.000Z","msg":"台灣會<br />\n嘈到家變個隻嘈"},{"pid":"012d503b042765c29641756d880d073c79a1ff91","tid":1253292,"uid":64191,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T15:04:19.000Z","msg":"試過去外國家庭屋企食飯，無論經濟、時事都有辯論，但真係純學術意見交流一樣，間中問我意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489b9d74d8c65cb019885e7d1c02b65702055493","tid":1253292,"uid":218203,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T15:04:42.000Z","msg":"美國好多後生仔支持侵侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75630a9ab3450f1b04be599b8ca17ee425af8b44","tid":1253292,"uid":213893,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"5f709eb38ccc5db693989da1ae3125e7cddaf857","tid":1253292,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:16:46.000Z","msg":"會唔會廢老前廢老後？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T15:07:26.000Z","msg":"留意脫歐<br />\n其實係會<br />\n不過肯撚定唔會用父母身份嚟強姦仔女政見<br />\n佢地仔女一大就理撚得你老竇定老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faed5592ffbeb4b90def5f53397e8b4d4deeb258","tid":1253292,"uid":118351,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5f709eb38ccc5db693989da1ae3125e7cddaf857","tid":1253292,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:16:46.000Z","msg":"會唔會廢老前廢老後？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T15:34:38.000Z","msg":"會, 廢老=baby-boomer (即係二戰後經濟起飛時出世嘅人)"},{"pid":"32ac78c7a95b2f650e02bcd3504ccc47bd1a2cb7","tid":1253292,"uid":53705,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T15:57:34.000Z","msg":"外國同香港唔同<br />\n<br />\n外國就算政見唔同, 但佢地內心都係想自己國家好<br />\n<br />\n香港既廢老根本就係想推香港去死"},{"pid":"611360bef0bbd3d9d49d07379701774411913457","tid":1253292,"uid":158499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:05:08.000Z","msg":"香港呢個地方，典型年輕人同典型廢老嘅爭拗，起因係香港得一個大電視台，廢老每日不智不覺間接受洗腦程序;<br />\n年輕人識上網，識吸收網上資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ea74e701eaf8fd3402213879f98223e21d990d","tid":1253292,"uid":235021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:12:27.000Z","msg":